    <item>
      <title>南非的联盟teeters预算显示裂谷扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-africa-s-coalition-teeters-as-budget-shows-widening-rift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的统治联盟有可能在其主要成员对拟议的税收增加的争议加深，使兰特的税收加剧之后，可能会破裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-africa-s-coalition-teeters-as-budget-shows-widening-rift</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 06:18:55 GMT</pubDate>
